                MOVE 'YES' TO ERROR-FOUND-SW.
           IF W-94-PARISH-CODE NOT NUMERIC
                MOVE ALL '*' TO W-ERROR-94-PARISH-CODE
                MOVE 'ERROR: INVALID PARISH CODE'
                    TO W-ERROR-3-DESCRIPTION
                MOVE 'YES' TO ERROR-FOUND-SW.
